  "detailed_description": "<h1>RECOMMENDED FOR YOU</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1919550/extras/a98eca45e548c50971a01d5675eaa033.poster.avif?t=1771944735\" width=616 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1919550/extras/a98eca45e548c50971a01d5675eaa033.webm?t=1771944735\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Meow meow meow mes amis! Cats are hidden in a unique lovely Paris scenario.<br>A short and pleasant experience in a big and lovely illustration! Start with a Beautiful monochromatic scenario, relax, and find all the cats to reveal the final colored art.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1919550/extras/663f83d617ebd310dbdc6bf43a5e3802.webp?t=1771944735\" width=24 height=17 /></span> <strong>More than 680 hidden objects to find!!!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1919550/extras/663f83d617ebd310dbdc6bf43a5e3802.webp?t=1771944735\" width=24 height=17 /></span> <strong>Play through different modes, find special cats, and unlock bonus levels!</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1919550/extras/62f9269cf362ecfc4ee0aa54bc7fd489.avif?t=1771944735\" width=616 height=174 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NORMAL MODE</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find 100 cats in fixed positions.<br></li><li>3 hints.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ADVANCED MODE</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find 150 cats in semi-random positions.<br></li><li> 8 Special cats that unlock Bonus Levels and give hints.<br></li><li> 16 city people to find and earn hints.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1919550/extras/560eb53b6616faa5b341baa665a38fa7.poster.avif?t=1771944735\" width=616 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1919550/extras/560eb53b6616faa5b341baa665a38fa7.webm?t=1771944735\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Bonus Levels with different sizes and numbers of kittens. One use of hint for helping.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Boulangerie:</strong> 50 kittens<br></li><li><strong>Catacombs: </strong>50 kittens<br></li><li><strong>Patisserie:</strong> 50 kittens<br></li><li><strong>Cabaret:</strong> 75 kittens<br></li><li><strong>Louvre:</strong> 100 kittens<br></li><li><strong>Versailles:</strong> 100 kittens</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1919550/extras/bf79fcdfb7a73622b84a384f44731966.webp?t=1771944735\" width=584 height=41 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Accessibility</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dark Mode<br></li><li>Invert Mouse Zoom<br></li><li>Mouse Drag Sensibility<br></li><li>Edge Screen Scrolling<br></li><li>Color Blindness</li></ul>",
